### ============================================
### 3. API RESERVAS DE HOTEL (Port 3002)
### ============================================

### GET - Listar reservas
GET http://localhost:3002/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST - Criar reserva (sucesso)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cliente": "Carlos Mendes",
  "checkin": "2025-11-01",
  "checkout": "2025-11-05",
  "tipo_quarto": "duplo"
}

###

### POST - Criar reserva (erro - checkout anterior ao checkin)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cliente": "Ana Silva",
  "checkin": "2025-11-10",
  "checkout": "2025-11-08",
  "tipo_quarto": "simples"
}

###

### POST - Criar reserva (erro - sem disponibilidade)
POST http://localhost:3002/api/reservas
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cliente": "Pedro Costa",
  "checkin": "2025-12-20",
  "checkout": "2025-12-25",
  "tipo_quarto": "suite"
}

###

### PUT - Atualizar reserva
PUT http://localhost:3002/api/reservas/10
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tipo_quarto": "suite",
  "checkout": "2025-11-06"
}

###

### DELETE - Cancelar reserva (não permitido após checkin)
DELETE http://localhost:3002/api/reservas/10
Content-Type: application/json

